<h3 id="install-the-app">Install the app</h3>

<p>Installing the app is extremely simple.</p>

<p>Open the <a href="https://apps.shopify.com/">Shopify App Store</a>, find the application and click Add app button.</p>

<p><span class="doc_image"><img src="/assets/images/start/2.png" alt="button add" /></span></p>

<p>With any installation option, you will be prompted to select a tariff plan when launching an app for the first time.</p>

<p>Follow the instructions from Quick Start after that..</p>

<h3 id="quick-start">Quick start</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Open the application.</li>
  <li>Create a preloader.</li>
  <li>Navigate to the Pages page and click Create new button. The new page will be created.</li>
</ul>

<p><span class="doc_image" id="createnew" onclick="showModal(this.getAttribute('id'))"><img src="/assets/images/start/createnew.gif" alt="createnew" /></span></p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Design a new page using ready-made blocks, or go to step №5.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Navigate to the Templates tab and click on the Restore default templates button. Standard templates will be downloaded.</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><span class="doc_image" id="restoredef" onclick="showModal(this.getAttribute('id'))"><img src="/assets/images/start/restoredef.gif" alt="restoredef" /></span></p>

<ul>
  <li>Select the necessary template, for example, “Simtech Demo” and upload it to your newly created page.</li>
</ul>

<p><span class="doc_image" id="simtechdemo" onclick="showModal(this.getAttribute('id'))"><img src="/assets/images/start/simtechdemo.gif" alt="simtechdemo" /></span></p>

<ul>
  <li>Find the page on the Pages tab and enable it.</li>
</ul>

<p><span class="doc_image" id="enable" onclick="showModal(this.getAttribute('id'))"><img src="/assets/images/start/enable.gif" alt="enable" /></span></p>
